OL,3,CBag of guns left outside London Mayor
OL,4,CSadiq Khan's home
OL,6,FA bag of guns was left outside London
OL,7,FMayor Sadiq Khan's home by armed
OL,8,Fpolice who were there to guard the
OL,9,Fproperty, it has emerged.
OL,11,FFive people have now been temporarily
OL,12,Fsuspended from frontline police duties
OL,13,Fas an investigation takes place.
OL,15,FThe bag was found by a passing member
OL,16,Fof the public by the kerb of a road in
OL,17,Fsouth London on Tuesday evening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
