OL,3,CBag of guns left outside London Mayor
OL,4,CSadiq Khan's home
OL,6,FInside was a MP5 semi-automatic
OL,7,FHeckler & Koch carbine, a Glock
OL,8,Fpistol, Taser and ammunition,
OL,9,Faccording to The Sun.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FThe Met's Directorate of Professional
OL,17,FStandards is reviewing what happened
OL,18,Fand said five officers have been
OL,19,Fremoved from frontline duties.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
