OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775416261
OL,3,CBag of guns left outside London Mayor
OL,4,CSadiq Khan's home
OL,6,F"At around 9.40pm, a member of the
OL,7,Fpublic called police after finding a
OL,8,Fbag containing Met-issued firearms and
OL,9,Fa Taser on a street in south London,"
OL,10,Fthe force said.
OL,12,F"Within seven minutes of the call to
OL,13,Fpolice, officers arrived at the scene
OL,14,Fand safely recovered the items.
OL,16,F"We are urgently reviewing the
OL,17,Fcircumstances of this incident and
OL,18,Frecognise the concern it may cause.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
