PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775416261
OL,3,CBag of guns left outside London Mayor
OL,4,CSadiq Khan's home
OL,6,F"At this stage it is believed the bag
OL,7,Fwas misplaced by on-duty officers a
OL,8,Fshort time before the member of the
OL,9,Fpublic located it.
OL,11,F"We recognise the concern this may
OL,12,Fcause and an internal review was
OL,13,Fimmediately launched into the
OL,14,Fcircumstances."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@OO]
