OL,3,CBag of guns left outside London Mayor
OL,4,CSadiq Khan's home
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Mayor of London Sir
OL,7,FSadiq said: "This is a very serious
OL,8,Fincident, which has been referred to
OL,9,Fthe Met's Directorate of Professional
OL,10,FStandards. The Met must now take all
OL,11,Fsteps to ensure an incident like this
OL,12,Fnever occurs again."
